name: Devour... Demand... DeFi.
description:
I photo myself in the mirror; then paint the photograph. By using "Me" as the subject of my art, I can get as bawdy or naughty, playful or silly as I desire. My art uses savage color in serene moments. I hope you like my exploration and play. I've created these CryptoGurls to humor, inspire, and turn you on... to the Metaverse. I'd be honored to be in your collection. xoRobbi

Longing to devour the weaknesses in old systems, we DEMAND Defi. Crypto is no cult; it's philosophy, and financial freedom for our new world. We join in community to make Catastrophic Love to the globe through Metcalf's Law::: bitcoin and beyond. Come : let's destroy the boomer base ideals. It's time to Orange Pill the world together.
